content: New Test cases @ https://fhir.github.io/latest-ig-publisher/test-cases.zip (v1.0.22). Changes: More validation examples to test various forms of invalid extension use, and cross version extensions
New Test cases @ https://fhir.github.io/latest-ig-publisher/test-cases.zip (v1.0.23). Changes: Add additional test - reslicing as a child of type slicing
New Test cases @ https://fhir.github.io/latest-ig-publisher/test-cases.zip (v1.0.24). Changes: Add a test for a type slicing case that lead to a stack overflow
New Test cases @ https://fhir.github.io/latest-ig-publisher/test-cases.zip (v1.0.25). Changes: Fix code system narrative generation poly-heirarchy test cases
New Test cases @ https://fhir.github.io/latest-ig-publisher/test-cases.zip (v1.0.26). Changes: Reorganize validator test manifest
New Test cases @ https://fhir.github.io/latest-ig-publisher/test-cases.zip (v1.0.27). Changes: 4.2.0 Release
New Test cases @ https://fhir.github.io/latest-ig-publisher/test-cases.zip (v1.0.28). Changes: Changes to the way CodeableConcept is validated
New Test cases @ https://fhir.github.io/latest-ig-publisher/test-cases.zip (v1.0.29). Changes: Additional test for snapshot generation and code system validation

New Test cases @ https://fhir.github.io/latest-ig-publisher/test-cases.zip (v1.0.31). Changes: Tests for reference validation of profiles, including circular references, and tests for consequential issues discovered
New Test cases @ https://fhir.github.io/latest-ig-publisher/test-cases.zip (v1.0.32). Changes: Tests for context invariants and memberOf
New Test cases @ https://fhir.github.io/latest-ig-publisher/test-cases.zip (v1.0.33). Changes: Fix test for contextInvariant usage
New Test cases @ https://fhir.github.io/latest-ig-publisher/test-cases.zip (v1.0.34). Changes: more test cases for extension context and example references
New Test cases @ https://fhir.github.io/latest-ig-publisher/test-cases.zip (v1.0.35). Changes: more test cases for slicing and validating
New Test cases @ https://fhir.github.io/latest-ig-publisher/test-cases.zip (v1.0.36). Changes: add test cases for constraining element part of choice, and not the choice
New Test cases @ https://fhir.github.io/latest-ig-publisher/test-cases.zip (v1.0.37). Changes: Fix test for constraining slices to also sort
New Test cases @ https://fhir.github.io/latest-ig-publisher/test-cases.zip (v1.0.38). Changes: Add test cases for assumeValidRestReferences
New Test cases @ https://fhir.github.io/latest-ig-publisher/test-cases.zip (v1.0.39). Changes: Add test cases for testing earch parameter type in CapabilityStatement
New Test cases @ https://fhir.github.io/latest-ig-publisher/test-cases.zip (v1.0.40). See release notes at https://fhir.github.io/latest-ig-publisher/release-notes-test-cases.html

New Release v1.0.41. Changes :

  • rename R5 FHIRPath tests to actually say R5, and add a test for doing is on empty collections

New Release v1.0.42. Changes :

  • Add a test case for a differential that caused an NPE in the snapshot-generator
  • Adjust test cases around lang/xml:lang (see https://www.w3.org/TR/i18n-html-tech-lang/#langvalues)
  • Fix validator tests around xhtml language to cover both lang and xml:lang (see https://www.w3.org/TR/i18n-html-tech-lang/#langvalues)
  • Add an additional validator test for multiple enableWhen conditions on a questionnaire item

New Release v1.0.43. Changes :

  • Update tests for generating lang as well as xml:lang
  • Add test case for search references in transactions

New Release v1.0.44. Changes :

  • Update R4 and R5 FHIR Path Patch tests per https://chat.fhir.org/#narrow/stream/179166-implementers/topic/FHIRPath.20Patch.20Test.20Cases

New Release v1.0.45. Changes :

  • Test for tim-9 bug in FHIRPath (Currently wrong outcome specified)
  • Slicing on patternCoding
  • Improve Code System property rendering

New Release v1.0.46. Changes :

  • Add tests for FHIRPath exists([crieria])
  • Add test for invariant that has a source

New Release v1.0.47. Changes :

  • Add new test case for checking that a Json Primitive is actually a list when it should be

New Release v1.0.48. Changes :

  • add test for Document missing meta.lastUpdated in R2/R3

New Release v1.1.0. Changes :

  • add test case for cross version snapshot test case - 1.4.0 extension profiling issue

New Release v1.1.2. Changes :

(no changes yet)

New Release v1.1.3. Changes :

  • Test case for bundle referene validation
  • Test cases for extension context
  • Test cases for required questionanire items

New Release v1.1.4. Changes :

  • Add test case for bad JSON
  • Add test cases for Measure/MeasureReport validation

New Release v1.1.5. Changes :

  • Re-organise supporting collateral for tests
  • More test cases for Measure/MeasureReport validation
  • Add additional questionnaire test cases
  • More tests around duplicate ids

New Release v1.1.6. Changes :

  • Add test case for partial version reference

New Release v1.1.7. Changes :

  • add test case for FHIRPath contexts for an extension in a Bundle

New Release v1.1.9. Changes :

  • add new test case for ICD-9-CM

New Release v1.1.10. Changes :

  • add more tests around questionnaire enableWhen

New Release v1.1.11. Changes :

  • Add test cases for profile slicing by type as an example
  • Add FHIRPath test cases for invalid use of and

New Release v1.1.12. Changes :

  • update for release of new FHIR version

New Release v1.1.13. Changes :

  • Add test case to check proper use of urn:ietf:rfc:3986 identifiers

New Release v1.1.14. Changes :

  • Start adding test cases for Conformance resource comparisons
  • Updates to test cases for v 4.4.0 releases
